   7:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_flash.c ****   *          functionalities of the internal FLASH memory:
   8:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_flash.c ****   *           + Program operations functions
